long_description: gr8work builders has teamed up with wendy and patrick mccann. they own a concrete construction company in southern california and nevada, bringing their extensive knowledge in construction and real estate sectors to the company. this combination of construction experience, professional design skills, and expert financial planning added to the gr8work team ensures the continuation of quality projects to the peninsula. we take pride in extending our family values to our customers, treating your projects with the utmost care and commitment to excellence. in 1977 bob founded gr8work builders. this passion for perfection led to bob affiliating with other trade contractors who cherish quality, service and have an extensive knowledge of remodeling. it all begins with an idea. we build custom accessory dwelling units perfectly designed for your needs. in-law suites, cottages, secondary units and more. for over 45 years, gr8work builders has specialized in residential remodeling, and we provide our customers with a service, not just a product.
